{"title" : "徒步穿越" ,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>徒步穿越是户外独立拓展项目之一。</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>是指除只借助一小部分交通工具外，大部分旅行区域靠徒步行走的一种户外活动。</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'>其以纯自然的高山景观等作为征服对象，以克服路途中重重障碍和限制条件，只能依靠团队合作的力量，最终到达终点为目</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'>标。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'><?xml:namespace prefix = 'o' ns = 'urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>金牌徒步穿越障碍设置，倾注和凝聚了金牌众合作伙伴全体团队的心血。障碍的目的性与安全性，地点测试、路线规划，金牌团队常年来往于大山间，山上的每一处花草树木，都与金牌教练结下了</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'>深厚的感情。冬季山高路滑，但为了障碍物及路线不被大雪掩盖，以备春天使用，需要定期上山清理，一条山脉全程清理下来，需要从早到晚整整一天时间。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>所以徒步穿越，是金牌全体教练员与企业团队共同完成的一次穿越！但团队每一次成功穿越后的欢呼，也为我们共同完成了一次心灵的穿越！</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><BR><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>穿越指标介绍：</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 11.95pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-left: 1.14gd'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>难度：★★☆</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><BR><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>强度：★★★</SPAN><BR><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>冒险指数：★★☆</SPAN><BR><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>风景指数：★★★☆</SPAN><BR><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>原始指数：★★★★</SPAN><BR><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>徒步距离：</SPAN>10-40<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>公里</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt'><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>附：徒步穿越注意事项</SPAN></B><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P><P class=MsoNormal style='MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>每一个参加者在出发前首先要清楚以下问题：你身体健康吗？你胆子小吗？在遇到危险时你会退缩吗？在别人需要帮助时你会伸出援助之手吗？</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>要了解徒步穿越的四大特性：</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>　　</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>1<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、富于求知、探索性。徒步穿越者每准备一次穿越活动，都要对穿越地区进行了解。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; mso-char-indent-count: -3.0'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>　　</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>2<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、有一定障碍难度。徒步穿越是一项综合性强、有一定难度的野外活动。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; mso-char-indent-count: -3.0'><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp; </SPAN>3 <SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、要有团队精神，乐于助人。同时，长途穿越者需要提前掌握一些相关的知识和技能，如天文、气象、地理、生物、生理、地质、物理、化学等知识。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; mso-char-indent-count: -3.0'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>　</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>4<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、 <STRONG><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'>环保。</SPAN></STRONG>徒步穿越是为了亲近大自然，所以做一次环保的旅行是热爱户外运动者最起码的道德标准。保护自然的生态平衡是大家的一份责任，有句话说的好：除了照片什么都别带走，除了脚印什么都别留下。</SPAN> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -3.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: #333333; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>几个常见问题：</SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.95pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -12pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -1.0; mso-para-margin-left: 1.14gd; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt'><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'><FONT face=宋体>1<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、卫生问题。在自然界就地如厕时要远离水源</SPAN>30<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>米，且在营地下风口，最好在方便地点稍微用土掩埋，以防止气味散发污染。还有野外用火，袭击野生动物，砍伐树木等都是破环自然的行为。 </SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>　</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>2<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、“某某到此一游”等刻字行为最好别留下。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -12pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -1.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp; </SPAN>3<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>迷路。不要脱离团队，擅自行动。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 17.95pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -6pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -.5; mso-para-margin-left: 1.14gd; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt'><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><FONT face=宋体>4<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、突然受伤（</SPAN></FONT><A href='http://zhidao.baidu.com/search?word=%E5%B4%B4%E8%84%9A&amp;fr=qb_search_exp&amp;ie=utf8' target=_blank><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='TEXT-DECORATION: none; COLOR: windowtext; text-underline: none'><FONT face=宋体>崴脚</FONT></SPAN></A><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>比较常见）或生急病。出行前清楚自己的身体状况，教练都携带需要的药</SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 17.95pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 12pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0; mso-para-margin-left: 1.71gd; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>品；发生</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><A href='http://zhidao.baidu.com/search?word=%E5%B4%B4%E8%84%9A&amp;fr=qb_search_exp&amp;ie=utf8' target=_blank><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='TEXT-DECORATION: none; COLOR: windowtext; text-underline: none'>崴脚</SPAN></A><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>时尽快作处理，根据严重程度听从指挥安排下山。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 12pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><FONT face=宋体>5<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、体力透支。提前几日注意活动身体，感觉体力不支必须告诉教练，教练会给予妥善安排。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P><P style='TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 24pt; TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>　</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma'>3<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、<STRONG><SPAN style='FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-WEIGHT: normal; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold'>团队精神</SPAN></STRONG>。在<SPAN class=kw>穿越</SPAN>中，集体的力量大于一切，每个人都要通过集体的合作才能战胜困难，共同分享成功的喜悦。集体<SPAN class=kw>穿越</SPAN>是体现个人与他人相互协作的能力以及团队合作精神的好机会，一次成功的集体<SPAN class=kw>穿越</SPAN>除了要求个人的野外生存技能外，最重要的是团队合作的精神。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>"}